QUALIFICATION: this is not a species of Microdiscula and is a tornid. However, the genus placement for this species is uncertain, although it could tentatively be included in Vitrinella which would make it a secondary homynym of Vitrinella vitrea Laseron, 1958. We prefer to keep this name in incertae sedis pending further revision. The genus level classification of this entire group requires major revision
